Součástí procesu výběru jsou také další kritéria ESG a principy globálního kompaktu OSN. Vybrané cenné papíry jsou váženy stejně v indexu. TER (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 0,31% P.A .. name: UBS S&P 500 Climate Transition ESG UCITS ETF hEUR acc
description_en: The UBS S&P 500 Climate Transition ESG UCITS ETF hEUR acc seeks to track the S&P 500® Climate Transition Base ESG (EUR Hedged) index. The S&P 500® Climate Transition Base ESG (EUR Hedged) index tracks US securities. Only companies with low carbon emissions and a high ESG (environmental, social and governance) rating are considered. The parent index is the S&P 500®. Currency hedged to Euro (EUR). The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.10% p.a.. The UBS S&P 500 Climate Transition ESG UCITS ETF hEUR acc is the only ETF that tracks the S&P 500® Climate Transition Base ESG (EUR Hedged) index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The UBS S&P 500 Climate Transition ESG UCITS ETF hEUR acc is a very small ETF with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 18 March 2024 and is domiciled in Ireland.

name: WisdomTree STOXX Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short
description_en: The WisdomTree STOXX Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short seeks to track the STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense Short Leverage (-3x) index. The STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense Short Leverage (-3x) index tracks the three times leveraged inverse performance of the STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense index on a daily basis. The STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense index tracks the performance of European companies that are engaged in the aerospace and defense industry. The ETN's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.85% p.a.. The ETN replicates the performance of the underlying index synthetically with a swap. The dividends in the ETN are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The WisdomTree STOXX Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short is a very small ETN with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETN was launched on 23 April 2025 and is domiciled in Ireland.
